  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the binchotan grill to 200 degrees Celsius.",
    "Cut the Manchego cheese into 1 inch cubes.",
    "Thread the cheese, bell peppers, and onions onto the skewers.",
    "Brush the skewers with olive oil and season with thyme and rosemary.",
    "Grill the skewers for 5 minutes on each side, or until crispy and golden brown.",
    "Deglaze the grill with lemon juice and honey.",
    "Serve the skewers hot, drizzled with the sweet sauce from the deglazed grill."
